      **  Read first Retail Account.
     C                   Read      CLOANCL                                81

      **  Do while Retail Accounts to be processed.
     C     *in81         Doweq     False                                        Begin Do_W_N81

      **  If Replication field has to be reset.
     C     *inu1         Ifeq      False                                        Begin *inu1

      **  Update Replication Indicator field.
     C                   Eval      REPI = *blank

      **  Update Customer Loans file record.
     C                   Update    CLOANCLF

      **  If printing of reports required.
     C                   Else                                                   Else *inu1

      **  Update Replication Indicator field.
     C                   Eval      REPI = 'C'

      **  Update Customer Loans file record.
     C                   Update    CLOANCLF

      **  Print Customer Loan informations on report.
     C                   Exsr      #Report

     C                   Endif                                                  End *inu1
     C                   Eval      RCOUNT = RCOUNT + 1

      **  Read next Customer Loan record.
     C                   Read      CLOANCL                                81

     C                   Enddo                                                  End Do_W_N81

      **  If printing of reports required.
     C     *inu1         Ifeq      True                                         Begin *inu1

      **  If at least one line has been printed.
     C     RCOUNT        Ifgt      0                                            Begin RCOUNT
     C                   Write     ENDPAG1

      **  Check that sufficient lines remain for the Format. If not,
      **  write out the Main Headings on a new page.
     C                   Eval      Rqdln1 = 4
     C                   Eval      Difln1 = Oflln1 - Prtln1
     C     Difln1        Ifle      Rqdln1                                       Begin Difln1
     C                   Write     HEADP1

     C                   Endif                                                  End Difln1

      **  Write out Trailer Format.
     C                   Write     TRAILP1

      **  Close Customer Loans COB changes Report printer file.
     C                   Close     RP1407P1

     C                   Endif                                                  End RCOUNT

     C                   Endif                                                  End *inu1

      **  Print Audit Report.
     C                   Exsr      #Audit

      **  End Program and Return.
     C                   Eval      *inlr = True
     C                   Return

