     C                   Call      'ZSFILE'
     C                   Parm      *Blanks       Seq               5
     C                   Parm                    Senty             3
     C                   Parm                    Sfile1
     C                   Parm                    Zsnum1            6 0
     C                   Parm                    Zserr             1

      **  If any Error occurred during ZSFILE processing, then return to the
      **  Calling Program.
     C     Zserr         Ifeq      'Y'                                          Begin Zserr
     C                   Eval      *inu7 = True
     C                   Eval      *inu8 = True
     C                   Eval      *inlr = True
     C                   Return
      *
     C                   Endif                                                  End Zserr
      *
     C                   Endsr
